What are the names of popular violinists whose last names start with N or Z, and what are their websites?

Here are some renowned violinists with last names that begin with either N or Z, along with their websites:

- **Itzhak Perlman**: Widely considered one of the greatest violinists of all time, Itzhak Perlman's website is https://www.perlmanmusicprogram.org/.

- **Sarah Chang**: Known for her virtuosic playing, Sarah Chang's official website is https://www.sarahchang.com/.

- **Hilary Hahn**: A Grammy-winning violinist, Hilary Hahn's website is https://www.hilaryhahn.com/.

- **Nikolaj Znaider**: Nikolaj Znaider, a Danish virtuoso, conductor, and pedagogue, can be found at https://www.nathanielsznaider.com/.

- **Nikolai Zinin**: Russian violinist Nikolai Zinin performs and teaches; his website is https://www.nikolaizinin.com/.

- **Frank Peter Zimmermann**: German violinist Frank Peter Zimmermann's website offers concert information and recordings at https://www.frank-peter-zimmermann.com/en/.
